title: After deducting the area of TDA, FSI will be available for the rest of the land in SDZ, as provided for the area in SDZ-as per clause (VI) (xii)
clause_text: After deducting the area of TDA, FSI will be available for the rest of the land in SDZ, as provided for the area in SDZ-as per clause (VI) (xii). In case of plots having area more than 2 ha in SDZ, no subdivision of plots shall be permitted.

source_pdf.text_snippet: After deducting the area of TDA, FSI will be available for the rest of the land in SDZ, as provided for the area in SDZ-as per clause (VI) (xii).
